    "body" : "<p>Try this</p>\n\n<pre><code> LayoutParams params = new LayoutParams(\n            LayoutParams.WRAP_CONTENT,      \n            LayoutParams.WRAP_CONTENT\n    );\n    params.setMargins(left, top, right, bottom);\n    yourbutton.setLayoutParams(params);\n</code></pre>\n"
